snippet.title: Card Sagas Wars
snippet.description:
preview with my project with Ahruon, a fighting game made with mugen with custom characters from various games made by us, right now it's in a very preliminary phase but this is somewhat what we have done so far

pd: sorry about the video quality, hope you like it though
